He is the greatest singer I have heard till now. There are other great singers but he is one of a kind. Not too sweet (Rahat) to be cloying not too harsh that you cannot hear in every mood. Hi is one that doesn't require you to be in any specific mood to hear him. And he can fucking sing in any range from top to bottom. Yet to imagine a kind of song that he cannot sing.

This song deserved more than a million views by now. 200-300 toh mere hi honge. I guess we only talk about good music but don't appreciate it.
